title: Multimedia Presentation on John Coltrane by Dr. Teodross Avery
description:
Multimedia Presentation on John Coltrane- From So What (1959) to Impressions (1965) 

Dr. Teodross Avery gives his Multimedia presentation on John Coltrane. Here, he presents a Lecture/Performance on one of the greatest artists of the twentieth century. 

Featured in the band are: 
Dr. Teodross Avery- tenor saxophone, lecturer
Benito Gonzalez- piano
Corcoran Holt- bass
Marvin "Bugalu" Smith- drums


Recorded at the National Jazz Museum in Harlem on Saturday, September 24th, 2016.

For booking contact info@teodrossavery.com
